Viceroy released a report which likened Capitec to a loan shark while Sarb announced that VBS Mutual Bank had been placed under curatorship. CAPE TOWN- Representatives of Capitec Bank and VBS Mutual are appearing before Parliament's finance portfolio committee. In January, US-based fund manager Viceroy released a report which likened Capitec to a loan shark. In March, the South African Reserve Bank announced that VBS Mutual Bank had been placed under curatorship with immediate effect. 